<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>For My Love ❤️</title>

<style>
body{
    background: linear-gradient(pink, #ffd6e7);
    text-align:center;
    font-family: "Comic Sans MS", cursive;
}

h1{
    color:#ff2e7a;
    font-size:40px;
}

p{
    font-size:20px;
    color:#444;
}

img{
    width:200px;
    border-radius:20px;
    margin:10px;
    box-shadow:0 0 15px pink;
}

.hearts{
    font-size:30px;
    animation: float 3s infinite;
}

@keyframes float{
    0%{transform:translateY(0);}
    50%{transform:translateY(-10px);}
    100%{transform:translateY(0);}
}

button{
    background:#ff4da6;
    border:none;
    padding:15px 25px;
    color:white;
    font-size:18px;
    border-radius:25px;
    cursor:pointer;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<h1>💖 For My Sweet Boyfriend 💖</h1>

<div class="hearts">💗 💕 💖 💘 💞</div>

<p>You are the cutest person in my life.  
Every moment with you is special.  
I love you forever! 💞</p>

<img src="photo1.jpg">
<img src="photo2.jpg">
<img src="photo3.jpg">

<br><br>

<button onclick="playMusic()">Play Our Song 🎶</button>

<audio id="song">
<source src="song.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<script>
function playMusic(){
document.getElementById("song").play();
}
</script>

<br><br>

<p>Made with love ❤️</p>

</body>
</html>

